### Create exercise
POST http://localhost:3000/exercises
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Push Ups",
  "reps": 15,
  "weight": 0,
  "unit": "lbs",
  "date": "2025-08-27"
}

### Get all exercises
GET http://localhost:3000/exercises

### Get exercise by id
# Replace {{id}} with a real _id from the previous responses
GET http://localhost:3000/exercises/{{id}}

### Update exercise
PUT http://localhost:3000/exercises/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Push Ups",
  "reps": 20,
  "weight": 0,
  "unit": "lbs",
  "date": "2025-08-28"
}

### Delete exercise
DELETE http://localhost:3000/exercises/{{id}}
